oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ripley snow scene
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of four men standing on the back of a snow plow in the street. The plow is being pulled by a tractor. A sign for the Westinghouse Appliances store is seen on the right.
